   * as well.
   *
   * Syntax:
   *
   *   math.stirlingS2(n, k)
   *
   * Examples:
   *
   *    math.stirlingS2(5, 3) //returns 25
   *
   * See also:
   *
   *    bellNumbers
   *
   * @param {Number | BigNumber} n    Total number of objects in the set
